text.section:
The cabinet shall:
Assist and cooperate with local governments and other agencies in the development and construction of local and regional bikeway projects;
Develop and publish policies, procedures, and standards for planning, designing, and constructing, maintaining, marking, and operating bikeways in the state, and for the safety of bicyclists, motorists, and the public;
Develop bikeway demonstration projects and safety training programs; and
Develop and construct a State Bikeway System.
